node.text: Treat your skin to #instantagerewind concealer. It conceals your bags and treats them; this formula makes the skin area appear radiant and refreshed in no time!

node.text: @emilydidonato on her first ever campaign with Maybelline and the iconic @cturlington! Like for part 2!💗

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Maybelline New York on August 19, 2021. May be an image of cosmetics.

node.text: Do you know your #fitmefoundation shade off the top of your head?🤔💭 Drop it in the comments below!⬇️ This foundation is perfect for normal to oily skin and comes in 40 shades! Find yours with our Foundation Finder tool at Maybelline.com!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Maybelline New York on August 18, 2021. May be a closeup of 1 person.

node.text:
We are loving @vanessa_gyimah go-to summer glam using Maybelline products!

To achieve this look, she used #fitmefoundation in the shade ‘370 deep bronze,' #lastingfix banana powder, #instantagerewind concealer in 'tan' and 'caramel,' #falsieslashlift mascara, The Blushed Nudes Eye Shadow Palette,  #hypereasyliner, and #Lifter Gloss in the shade 'crystal.' #regram #mnyitlook

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Maybelline New York on August 18, 2021. May be an image of cosmetics.

node.text: If you like smooth, clean lashes, #snapscara is the perfect mascara for you! This easy-on, easy-off formula applies effortlessly to deliver clump-free volume in an instant and removes in a snap! 😱

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Maybelline New York on August 18, 2021. May be a closeup of cosmetics.

node.text: All smiles in our #superstayinkcrayon shade ‘ground breaker’! Drop a ❤️ below if you’d rock this shade!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Maybelline New York on August 18, 2021. May be an image of cosmetics.

node.text: Feelin’ spicy?🌶 Kick up the heat in the last few weeks of summer with our #superstaymatteink Spiced Edition. Shown here is shade ‘innovator’.
